org.jscsi.parser.datasegment.OperationalTextKey

Packages that use OperationalTextKey
org.jscsi.initiator This package contains all the core classes to provide an easy and usable iSCSI (RFC 3720) initiator. 
org.jscsi.initiator.connection This package contains all the states of a connection and all phases of the iSCSI (RFC 3720) implementation. 
org.jscsi.parser.datasegment This package provides all main classes which are needed to deserialize and serialize all the attached data segments of messages defined by the iSCSI Standard (RFC 3720).
